    <description>&gt; # [color = &quot;gray&quot;] Reaper [/color] :shield:
&gt; **[color = &quot;gray&quot;] Neutral Killer [/color]**
&gt; 
&gt; Passive 1: Consume soul - If you would die at night you will consume a soul to heal yourself. You start with 4 souls.
&gt;
&gt; Passive 2: Gilded Bones: You can step up as King as though you had Royal Blood. You will keep Reap as a secondary ability if you become psycho king. As king it will no longer give you souls however.
&gt;
&gt; Day ability 1: Chill - Target player is silenced and cannot vote for the rest of the day. (2 soul)
&gt;
&gt; Day ability 2: Dark Words - Edit the reaped player&#39;s logs. (1 soul)
&gt;
&gt; Night ability 1: Reap - Kill target player and gain a soul. Bypasses healing. They will seem alive until after the next night. You will immediately see their class and logs. (Unlimited)
&gt;
&gt; Night ability 2: Gather Darkness - Kill target player and gain a soul. Bypasses healing and death immunity. You will secretly prevent anyone from occupying or redirecting you tonight. They will seem alive until after the next night. You will immediately see their class and logs. (2 souls)</description>
    
